<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_92b767dd09e6.aspx"><b>我行其野</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson92b767dd09e6">
<p>我行其野，蔽芾其樗。婚姻之故，言就尔居。尔不我畜，复我邦家。<br />我行其野，言采其蓫。婚姻之故，言就尔宿。尔不我畜，言归斯复。<br />我行其野，言采其葍。不思旧姻，求尔新特。成不以富，亦祗以异。</p>
</div>
